<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Provisional Vetting of DPR</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .page {
            background-color: white;
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .border-frame {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 2px dotted #333;
            padding: 4px;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .pattern-border {
            flex-grow: 1;
            border: 1px double #333;
            padding: 40px 50px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Standard Reference Decorative Borders */
        .page::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px;
            left: 5px;
            right: 5px;
            bottom: 5px;
            border: 2px solid #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .page::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            bottom: 10px;
            border: 4px double #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Watermark standard */
        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 80%;
            opacity: 0.1;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .watermark img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .content-area {
            font-size: 11.5pt;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header-logo {
            height: 80px;
            width: auto;
        }

        .doc-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 13pt;
        }

        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .list-item {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .sub-list {
            margin-left: 25px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .date-line {
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .sig-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
        }

        .digital-note {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            .page {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
            }

            .pattern-border {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="page">
        <div class="border-frame">
            <div class="pattern-border">

                <!-- Watermark -->
                <div class="watermark">
                    <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Watermark">
                </div>

                <div class="content-area">

                    <!-- Header Logo -->
                    <div class="logo-container">
                        <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Webel Logo" class="header-logo">
                    </div>

                    <!-- Document Header -->
                    <div class="doc-title">
                        Provisional Vetting of DPR of IT&ITeS (Application Number: <%= data?._application_number %>)
                    </div>

                    <!-- Intro Paragraph -->
                    <div class="list-item">
                        A Note on Project Report of <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._company_name %>
                        </span> proposal of building an IT&ITeS Unit at <%= data?._project_location %>.
                    </div>

                    <!-- Point 1 -->
                    <div class="list-item">
                        1. The project is proposed by <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._company_name %> (PAN: <%= data?._company_pan %>)
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Point 2 with sub-points -->
                    <div class="list-item">
                        2. (i) <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._company_name %>
                        </span> intends to build an IT based Project under IT&ITeS activity.

                        <div class="sub-list">
                            (ii) The activities/businesses as given in the <span class="bold">Declaration Letter (UDIN:
                                <%= data?._declaration_letter_udin %>)</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="sub-list">
                            (iii) The proposed application to be pursued in these premises is coverd under IT&ITeS
                            activity as notified by IT&E Dept., vide <span class="bold">notification <%=
                                    data?._it_notification_no %> dated <%= data?._it_notification_date %> (UDIN: <%=
                                            data?._it_notification_udin %>)</span>.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Point 3 -->
                    <div class="list-item">
                        3. This note addresses the technical aspects of the project report. Financial and commercial
                        viability/feasibility review is not attempted in this report.
                    </div>

                    <!-- Date -->
                    <div class="date-line">
                        Date: <%= data?._current_date %>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Signature Block -->
                    <div class="signature-block">
                        <span class="sig-title">Authorised Signatory</span>
                        <span class="sig-title">For Managing Director, Webel</span>
                        <div class="digital-note">(This document is digitally signed and does not require physical
                            signature)</div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>